# 17 - Debate Simulator (Multi-Agent with Profiles)
# Simulate a debate using fast models for rapid back-and-forth

NAME debate
INPUT topic
INPUT rounds DEFAULT 3

AGENT pro FROM agents/optimist.md REQUIRES "fast"
AGENT con FROM agents/devils-advocate.md REQUIRES "fast"

GOAL opening "Present the debate topic: $topic. Frame the key question and stakes."
GOAL conclude "Summarize both sides and identify the strongest arguments and key tensions. Save the debate transcript to debate-output.md."

CONVERGE debate_rounds "Present arguments for and against $topic, then respond to opposing arguments with counterpoints. Continue until arguments are exhausted or positions are well-established. Output CONVERGED when the debate has reached a natural conclusion." USING pro, con WITHIN $rounds

RUN setup USING opening
RUN debate USING debate_rounds
RUN wrap_up USING conclude
